      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true with upgraded polyurethane bushings, and the cooling system has been refreshed with a high-flow water pump. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its age, the powertrain and chassis dynamics are exceptionally tight, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
